name: Miz Pursey's Cupcake Purse for girls
description: Miz Pursey’s Cupcake Purse is all in fun. Every little girl wants to carry a purse like Mommy.  This little 8”x8”  cupcake is perfect for holding all of her treasures !!!  It is fully lined and has a velcro closure.  The cake and frosting come in a variety of colors.  View at   http://www.mpaceproductions.com

name: Harriet the Hair Accessory Queen
description: Harriet is a stationary doll that sits on your dresser and holds all your hair accessories.  She has a print dress,  an apron with pockets for scruntchies,  two long braids for barrettes and bows,  a crocheted hat for clips,  two long arms for headbands and two mittens to hold ribbons.   She is 12” tall and her hands are about 12” apart. She has a big smile just for you and comes in many colors. She can be seen  at  http://www.mpaceproductions.com  Please come visit and see our fun !!!

name: Baby-to-Go cradle purse w/doll
description: Baby-To-Go is a hand crocheted purse that opens flat into a baby bassinet. It comes with a baby, a blanket, a  diaper,  and a gown.  This purse is approximately 7” x 5” x  4”  and will go anywhere with your child. Excellent choice for a church purse,  travel toy,  vacation entertainment, etc.  Will keep your little one quiet and entertained.  Comes in a variety of colors.  View all at   mpaceproductions.com

name: My New Friend cloth body American rag doll
description: My  New Friend doll is designed for play NOT display. The doll is hale and hearty and expects to go where your child goes and do what your child does.  If you hug the doll she will hug you back. She has a dress, pantaloons, a pinafore, shoes and socks which are all removable and have velcro, elastic and laces. She is about 18”-20”  tall and other than scissors, she has no natural enemies. She will play all day and then keep the “goes bump in the night” away.  If she “accidentally” takes a dip in the tub, bag her and put her in the dryer. She plans on being a lifetime friend and listens very well without judgment. View her and all her pals at  mpaceproductions.com
